  "1901990": {
    "name": "Machine Gun Fury",
    "steam_appid": 1901990,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/b5efdff692f883768f7f32728bb7cc1b.avif?t=1772039081\" width=1170 height=354 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当暴政掌控一切……总得有人扣动扳机。<strong>Machine Gun Fury</strong> 是对经典街机军事射击游戏的大胆复兴——没有掩体系统，没有道德辩论，只有纯粹依靠反应的疯狂屠戮。你、你的扳机手指，以及有限的手雷，对抗整支军队。如果你曾在街机经典中一路扫射成长，欢迎重返前线，士兵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/53c4c1600c5a0424b2ae6faa280e2daa.poster.avif?t=1772039081\" width=1168 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/53c4c1600c5a0424b2ae6faa280e2daa.webm?t=1772039081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/53c4c1600c5a0424b2ae6faa280e2daa.mp4?t=1772039081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >凭借敏锐的反应、强大的火力和有限的手雷，杀出重围。解放8个爆炸性区域，面对铺满全屏的首领、无情的敌人浪潮以及高强度的run-and-gun动作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/eab426f467a81a0cde5ead28c0fb8346.poster.avif?t=1772039081\" width=1168 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/eab426f467a81a0cde5ead28c0fb8346.webm?t=1772039081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/eab426f467a81a0cde5ead28c0fb8346.mp4?t=1772039081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身三名武装到牙齿、势不可挡的战士，让暴政屈服：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gunner Jimbo</strong> —— 行走的突击部队。为压制火力而生，绝不妥协。他一旦停止射击，必有大爆炸发生。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Suzi Uzi</strong> —— 迅捷、战术性强且冷酷无情。不浪费子弹。不曾失手。永不停步。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mini-Gun Floyd</strong> —— 持续火力的化身。当枪管开始旋转，战场只剩回忆。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三名战士。一项不可能的任务。无尽的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/b2e97820b2b1e3cdbfc06b3f76717053.poster.avif?t=1772039081\" width=1168 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/b2e97820b2b1e3cdbfc06b3f76717053.webm?t=1772039081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/b2e97820b2b1e3cdbfc06b3f76717053.mp4?t=1772039081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >步战或驾驶重型武装载具——坦克、战斗艇、战斗越野车。释放完整的军用武器库，引发连锁爆炸，将敌方据点化为废墟。凡是会动的——全部消灭。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/3af42ee2494610f6505c93edf1de3980.poster.avif?t=1772039081\" width=1168 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/3af42ee2494610f6505c93edf1de3980.webm?t=1772039081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901990/extras/3af42ee2494610f6505c93edf1de3980.mp4?t=1772039081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高速<strong>俯视与横版run-and-gun玩法</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完整武器库，带来大规模破坏与惊人击杀数</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >融合现代强化效果的正统8-bit像素画面</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可破坏场景、屏幕震动、粒子特效与多层视差背景</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >受SID启发的爆炸性配乐，如同音量开到最大的街机机台</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >按下Start。扣动扳机。感受Fury。</p>",
